Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: Whether a worker is assigned to a specific team

Name: select_feature_for_release
Description: Whether a feature is included in the next release plan

Name: assign_story_points
Description: The number of story points assigned to a user story

Name: set_sprint_duration
Description: The duration of a sprint in days

Name: allocate_budget_to_feature
Description: The amount of budget allocated to develop a feature

Name: team_velocity_target
Description: The target velocity for a team in the next sprint

Name: start_sprint_date
Description: The start date of a sprint

Name: worker_availability_percent
Description: The percentage of time a worker is available for project work

Name: assign_task_priority
Description: The priority level of a task

Name: number_of_sprint_reviews
Description: The number of sprint reviews planned for a release
